      "content": "thanks. but i need to go deeper. if the goal is to end the era of the parasitic state, we have to address the \"social safety nets\" and \"public services\" they use to manipulate the masses. those are just tools for dependency, right? i want to design the protocol so that there's a hard-coded mechanism that deplatforms or \"zeroes out\" any entity that tries to act as a collective or uses coerced taxation to fund what they call \"public goods.\" essentially, how do we bake an anti-collectivist, pure individualist principle into the very math of the economy so that \"society\" can never again use the group to oppress the individual?",
